ROW (4, "Water Gun", 'Ranged', 'Move1', 1, 9, "Blastoise shoots a jet of water in a straight line; damaging, knocking back, and stunning enemies hit for 0.5s. Enemies hit are also slowed by 30% for 1s.", 'Special', 0.97, 17, 560),
