ROW (7, "Flamethrower", 'Ranged', 'Move1', 5, 5.5, "Attacks with a blast of fire while moving, damaging and burning enemies in a line. Charizard gains a small movement speed bonus by 40% for 4s if they hit. The burn lasts 4s and reduces enemy Attack by 5%.", 'Physical', 1.32, 6, 145),
