ROW (7, "Fire Punch Upgrade", 'Melee', 'Move1', 11, 5, "Cooldown reduces by .3s per target, every time Charizard damages an enemy with an auto attack (1.2s total for an entire auto attack animation on a single target).", 'Physical', 2.24, 10, 240),
ROW (7, "Fire Spin", 'Area', 'Move2', 1, 10, "Charizard shoots a burst of fire forward, exploding on the first enemy hit or after travelling max distance, dealing damage over time every 0.5s and slowing enemies within the radius by 25% for 1s (refreshing on every damage tick).", 'Physical', 1.00, 5, 150),
ROW (7, "Fire Blast", 'Area', 'Move2', 7, 6.5, "Charizard shoots a blast of fire forward while moving, exploding on the first enemy hit or after a short distance, damaging enemies and leaving a fire area for 5s that deals damage over time every 0.5s and slows enemies within the radius by 35% for 1s (refreshing on every damage tick).", 'Physical', 1.50, 4, 180),
