ROW (15, "Drill Peck", 'Melee', 'Move1', 5, 6, "Dodrio strikes forward with their sharp beaks multiple times, dealing damage to enemies hit. If used with a full sprint gauge, consume the sprint gauge and dash forward while striking with their sharp beaks multiple times, dealing damage to enemies hit and shoving them. During this dash, Dodrio receives 20% reduced damage.", 'Physical', 0.84, 2, 80),
