ROW (19, "Leaf Tornado", 'Ranged', 'Move1', 4, 9, "Eldegoss conjures a tornado full of leaves launching it in a designated direction. The tornado damages enemies and creates a path of wind that increases the movement speed of allies that touch it by 55% for 1.5s, refreshing as long as they are on the path. When the tornado reaches max distance, the path damages enemies on the path a second time. The haste path lasts for 4s.", 'Special', 1.06, 6, 240),
